luations declared a preference for the output images of the algorithm. We\ndescribe here a low-cost method for companding the HDR images with the ability\nto facilitate resections of mandibular lesions by providing optimal boundary\ndefinition.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 30 Mar 2020 16:07:03 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-03-31"}
