 to find optimal hyperparameters during the\ntraining phase. As application case, the problem of electricity load time\nseries forecasting has been addressed, showing quite remarkable performance.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 30 Mar 2020 17:10:02 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 16 Apr 2020 11:28:04 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-08-03"}
